headline: Palo Alto's forecasts signal AI boost for cybersecurity tools, shares rise
summary: (Reuters) -Palo Alto Networks (PANW) forecast fiscal 2026 revenue and profit above analysts' estimates on Monday, betting on growing demand for its artificial intelligence-powered cybersecurity solutions, sending its shares up 5% in extended trading.
